    "title": "Walk-in Drive Category Manager at Noise Global Group",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Noise Global Group. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Category Manager to strengthen our Mysuru-based team.\n\nAbout Noise Global Group:\nNoise Global Group is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mysuru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Noise Global Group!",
